            <p>Research Agora skills are <strong>agent-agnostic</strong> — while designed for Claude Code, they work with any LLM coding tool. Skills follow the <a href="https://agentskills.io" target="_blank" rel="noopener">AgentSkills.io</a> standard and can be converted for Cursor, Gemini CLI, and GitHub Copilot.</p>
